But what makes us one happy family?

node.text:
Some days I wish I can freeze time just so that I can capture some extra moments from Aaru’s 
childhood. As parents, @anitahassanandani and I, try our best to make the most of his growing years
because before we know it he will be flying out of our little nest and having a life of his own sooner 
than it seems.
And that’s why we have an unsaid rule set for the both of us as parents - There is nothing more 
important in this world than Aaravv. ​
#ItTakes2 by @PampersIndia is an eye-opener for many fathers, young and old alike. I urge everyone
out there to watch and share this film, and pledge to spend quality time with your baby while you 
have the chance.
#ItTakes2 #PampersIndia #EqualParenting #AMessageFromDad #PampersPremiumCare

node.text:
First ones are always special! 

When i first got into creating VFX content back in 2020, i dint realise how mainstream a revenue line it would become for @eipimedia … Today 60% of our branded projects require some sort of VFX integration… 

Fast Forward 2yrs, and today we are rolling out our first ever motion capture video, made entirely using the @hellorokoko body suit. By no means is the video anywhere close to what we would have liked. Hell, we are still figuring how to connect the suit to the system!! But, it’s a first, and we love the fact we are opening up a world of possibilities hereon. 

Going forward, We envisage a lot of branded content on social media integrating interesting elements using this technology and we are calling upon all our partners to give this a go …
